## Using $(environment) for app-foo/bar
# app-foo/bar clang/hardened

## Clang: Advanced Setup (https://wiki.gentoo.org/wiki/Clang#Advanced_examples)
# clang/hardened: build with a hardened Clang environment
# clang/chromium-hardened: tweaked hardening env for chromium
dev-lang/spidermonkey clang/hardened
net-p2p/qbittorrent clang/hardened
net-libs/libtorrent-rasterbar clang/hardened
www-client/firefox clang/hardened
www-client/librewolf clang/hardened
www-client/ungoogled-chromium clang/chromium-hardened
